(254, 'Tell me about the Custom Plan presets (Copy Website and E-Commerce)', 'The Custom Plan at Rielcode allows you to build your own package tailored to your needs, including options for copying an existing website design and e-commerce functionalities! However, these specific features are not predefined presets but rather customizable options that you can include based on your requirements.', NULL, 'chat', NULL, NULL, '2026-05-12 02:48:30'),
